metadata.name: Dr. Molo
metadata.description:
Congratulations! We at Libby are thrilled to announce that you have been selected to receive a unique NFT, granting you access to a coveted seat at the table.

As a founder of this innovative web3 record label, I am proud to be at the forefront of the music industry's transition to the decentralized world of blockchain. And I am honored to have you join us on this journey.

Your NFT represents not only a symbol of recognition for your passion and dedication to the world of music, but also a tangible representation of your influence and contribution to our collective success. With it, you will have a voice in shaping the future of our label, and the opportunity to be a part of the exclusive community of artists, fans, and industry leaders who are leading the charge in this exciting new era.

Thank you for your continued support and contribution to our mission. I look forward to working with you to shape the future of music.

Best regards,  
OG Dan
